Package: cdtmbnma
Type: Package
Title: Component, Dose, and Time Network Meta-Analysis with Dose-Dependent Interaction
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Tyler", "Pitre", email = "pitretmed@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Arm-based component network meta-analysis that decomposes each
    treatment arm into component-specific dose-response curves and models the
    interaction between two components as a function of the doses of both, a
    dose-dependent interaction surface. Supports continuous and binary outcomes;
    additive, bilinear, and saturating (general pharmacodynamic interaction)
    surfaces; study-level random effects; and prediction of relative effects at
    dose combinations that no trial observed. Estimation uses Stan through
    'cmdstanr' or 'rstan'.
